data.description: The sellers are eager and poised for a swift transaction. "NEW" carpet and interior painting underway!    Charming Home in Winchester Estates, Lakeland, FL.    Property Overview:     • Size: Sprawling over 1,915 sq. ft.   • Rooms: 4 expansive bedrooms & 2 immaculate bathrooms.   • HOA: Enjoy the rarity of a VERY LOW HOA.   • Price: Undoubtedly the best priced home in Winchester Estates!    Interior Features:Step inside to appreciate:     • A spaciously conceived floor plan that effortlessly flows.   • A open kitchen concept leading to an expansive family lounge with pleasing views of your commodious, fenced backyard.   • Beyond the kitchen, find three well-lit bedrooms, a polished bathroom, convenient laundry room, and generous closet/storage areas.   • The family room beckons you towards the stately main bedroom, showcasing towering ceilings and an enormous walk-in closet. The ensuite bath is a haven with a deep soaker tub, a separate shower, and a dual vanity.    Exterior & Additional Features:     • Slide open the rear doors to discover a welcoming lanai, perfect for alfresco dining, leisure sitting, or relishing the captivating sunsets.   • Enjoy the vast backyard encompassed with a privacy fence          .       Recently constructed shed offering that much-needed extra storage space.   • To top it off, this gem is equipped with a brand-new dishwasher and a ROOF installed in 2021.    Given the exceptional value, this property might fly off the listings soon! Don’t let this chance slip away. Contact me ASAP for a viewing appointment! ????
